One trick against the wizards is to pull them, then use Divine Aura, as they will usually chain cast towards the beginning of the fight.<br>
<br>
Katta graveyard is really easy and safe. Not sure of the level requirement though. Just invis to undead, then run around the graveyard till one pops. If you get two, don't attack, they will despawn and you can try again. Pull well back to the gate/entrance. Root and nuke. From personal experience, Don't get cocky and pull a gargoyle from the steps........<br>
<br>
Traks teeth, near the Emerald jungle zone. Pacify and pull from the ruins. This is tougher but doable in upper 40's I think. I dinged 51 there.<br>
<br>
Spectre Island in Oasis is the best loot I've found. Start on the side of the island where the boat is. Root that one and nuke away. <br>
<br>
I'd say Guk was the best combo of exp and loot. Spectre Isand was the most convenient, best loot, and okay exp. Traks / Katta are a toss up. To far to run for mediocre loot / exp.<br>
<br>
If you get cocky in guk, Invis to undead and jump into the safe hall. Pacify everything and pull. It's very exciting..heh. Just keep gate memmed.<br>
<br>
Convince a Mage to go to L Guk with you. (If not more) Mage/Cleric duo is Great.<br>
